{
  "stem": "3022.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we tried very hard to give them all the wisdom, the camp wisdom that we possessed, which they didn't have.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We tried to tell them not to get in line the second times, because the kapo would recognize him and administer beating.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They used to trade their bread rations for cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they used to get sick and die from hunger.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They were not conditioned the way we were conditioned.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We were conditioned-- 1944, we were already five years of war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we gradually became-- those of us who were alive, we acquired certain savvy that these people were lacking.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The other thing that now I remember, we worked in a factory where we were sorting out nuts and bolts.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And that particular factory, it's the only time we were bombed by the Americans.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And several of us were killed, and some SS.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we were actually-- we were happy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We lost people, we were rejoicing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "That particular day, we were rejoicing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "From that camp, we used to go on a detail to another factory in a place called Horgau.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We used to go by train there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And my father worked there, and apparently he ruined something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He was not a mechanic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I remember before we were going back to the train station, there was my father hanging by his arms.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And this was one of the hardest things that I had to endure, to stay in line and look at my father hanging and controlling myself not to break out from the line and trying to help him.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And my father-- in his eyes-- they made sure that he hung.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "His feet were like six inches from the ground, and he was suspended in the air.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
